				Well its about time.  Yes roleplayers unite everquest is really dull without it do doubt.  I mean it dosn't make alot of difference whether you are swinging at a fire beetle or a hill giant.  Thats about the same thing.  Get close push 'A' on the keyboard.  Maybe cast a spell or two.  Its the same.  But roleplay, now its a different world.  My bard follows the goddess of love and stands in cities and speaks poems and tales of love and its sacrafice.  My shadow knight, huh he'll rip the throat from a halfling to eat his muffin.  XP not withstanding, thats right I see a good char somewhere, if I can take him I do xp or no xp.  Unfortuantly playing true evil is limited by rules of conduct, otherwise he would truly be evil.  Anyway good background.
